{"title":"春节（外二首）","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":2,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春节（外二首）\t顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有锣鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有爆竹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从废墟中飘起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有声音的烟……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颤抖的老人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞咽着一颗颗泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是他今年的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一顿早餐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然，他的泪痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化为惊喜的笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一队子弟兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到这残破的庄前……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨夜的炮声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊走了桃园的主人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨风吹散硝烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃子依然结得繁盛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饥渴的士兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在树下打盹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃子的香气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘进他们的梦……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒来，到溪边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝了几口水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们又踏上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥远的征程……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慰问"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一个漆黑的夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"士兵们摸进山沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傍着一块块岩石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织一个个梦……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒来，在步枪上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂满慰问袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像是丰满的果实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垂挂在树梢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子在身边围绕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘在身后轻笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇救会挑来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛着开水的水挑……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}